ad","description":"The preload plugin watches registered link elements via \nand proactively loads pages before the user clicks.\nIt respects network conditions and supports three strategies."},{"id":"/","title":"Home","description":"Qute is a lightweight hypermedia library built around the\nView Transitions API.\nIt lets you declaratively fetch and swap page fragments with smooth, typed transitions —\nno full page reloads, no virtual DOM."}]}